T hings can’t be hidden forever and that’s the lesson Ona’s mum Faith on House Of Zwide will learn very soon. The secret about who is Ona’s real father is on the verge of coming out. And to prevent the secret from being revealed, Faith and Isaac need to come up with a large amount of money to pay off private investigator Jonas, who worked with Faith many years ago. Jonas is under financial strain as business is no longer booming and he has decided to blackmail Faith and Isaac with the information he has about the identity of Ona’s father. Knowing that Faith would do anything to keep the dark secret that could end her marriage, it will be interesting to see how things pan out, and whether she will give Jonas the money or eliminate him like others in the past. ALSO READ |NEW SHOW ON TEENAGE PREGNANCY On The Queen, things are tricky between power couple Vuyiswa and Hector. Vuyiswa, who has been wanting to have a baby for a while, has finally received the good news that she is pregnant. But her happiness is short-lived as Hector doesn’t want more children. How will things pan out between the couple? Will she terminate her pregnancy just to keep her husband happy? On Skeem Saam, things aren’t looking good for the Magongwas. The more they try to hide the corruption they’re involved in to get the tender at the university, the more things get out of hand for the family. During a heated argument, Alfred pushed Alfios off a cliff and fled the crime scene, leaving him unconscious. He ran back home to tell his wife what happened and she suggested that they cover up the crime. Will they get away with it?